    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>(L) In Christi nomine. Breve pro futuris temporibus securitatis ac
                        firmitatis ad memoriam habendam vel retinendam, qualiter factum est in monte
                        de <rs key="#Castle">castello</rs> quod vocatur <placeName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Residential #Castle #Count" ref="#places/3203"
                            >Salamarzana</placeName>, in presentja hominum, quorum nomina subter
                        legentur. <persName key="#Count" ref="#people/3201">Ugo</persName> et
                            <persName key="#Count" ref="#people/3202">Lotherius</persName>
                        <rs key="#Count">comiti</rs>, germani filii bone memorie <persName
                            key="#Count" ref="#people/3200">Ughicionis</persName>
                        <rs key="#Count">magni comitis</rs>, per virgam quam tenebant in manibus
                        dederunt et tradiderunt <persName key="#Priests"><name ref="Iohannes"
                                >Iohanni</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Priests">presbitero</rs> custodi atque rectori <rs
                            key="#Hospitals">ospitali</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Hospitals" ref="#juridical_persons/3203"><placeName
                                ref="#places/3215" key="#Hospitals">Rosaie</placeName></orgName>,
                        videlicet omne <rs key="#Bonus/Malus_usus">usum</rs> et obedientjam et
                        redditum seu <rs key="#Profits_of_justice">placitum et districtum</rs> atque
                            <rs key="#Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters">glandaticum</rs>, quod
                        ipsi comiti (sic) sunt acepturi de <rs key="#Casae/cassinae_massaricie"
                            >sorte et re illa massaricia</rs>, posita in loco qui dicitur <placeName
                            ref="#places/3210"
                            key="#Casae/cassinae_massaricie #Fiscal_property #Profits_of_justice #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters #Bonus/Malus_usus"
                            >ad Putheum</placeName> et in eius finibus, que recta est per
                                <persName><name ref="Lambertus">Lanbertum</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name ref="Marcus">Marcum</name></persName> germanos et
                                <persName><name ref="Bonitius">Bonitjcum</name></persName> et per
                        filium <persName><name ref="Teutius">Teuzonis</name></persName>. Item
                        dederunt et tradiderunt ei tres sol(idos) denariorum Lucensium, quos
                        predicti comiti per singulos annos pro carne sunt acepturj a <persName><name
                                ref="Brunus">Bruno</name></persName> et <persName><name
                                ref="Iohannes">Iohanne</name></persName> filiis quondam
                                <persName><name ref="Omicius de Sancto Vito">Homici de <placeName
                                    ref="#places/3212">Sancto Vito</placeName>,</name></persName> et
                        duodecim denarios a filiis <persName><name ref="Iohannes"
                            >Iohannis</name></persName> quondam <persName><name ref="Begitius"
                                >Begicti</name></persName>, ut a modo in antea sint in potestate
                        suprascripti Iohannis presbiteri suorumque successorum vel rectorum ipsius
                        ospitali habendi et tenendi, sine omni predictorum comitum suorumque heredum
                        contraditjone vel molestatjone, donec ipsi centum sexaginta sol(ido)s
                        Lucensium denariorum bonorum non solverint ad partem predicti ospitali. Si
                        vero solverint, predicte res revertant et deveniant in dominio et potestate
                        predictorum comitum et suorum heredum sine omni controversia. Unde predicti
                        comiti obligaverunt se suosque heredes adversum prenominatum Iohannem
                        presbiterum suosque successores vel rectores ipsius ospitali ut si, ante
                        quam suprascriptos sol(ido)s solvant, res predictas eis abstulerint vel
                        minuaverint aliquo ingenio, et eis quiete et pacifice habere et tenere non
                        concesserint, quod componere debeant predicti comiti et sui heredes eid[e]m
                        Iohanni presbitero vel suis successoribus ad partem ipsius ospitali penam
                        boni argenti libras viginti. Hoc factum est <rs key="#Witness">in
                            presentja</rs>
                        <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Bulgarellus"
                            >Bulgarelli</name></persName> filii quondam <persName><name ref="Carbo"
                                >Carbonis</name></persName> et <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Martinus">Martini</name></persName> filii <persName><name
                                ref="Ragibertus">Ragimberti</name></persName> atque <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Walfredus">Vualfredi de <placeName
                                    ref="#places/3216">Spichello</placeName></name></persName> filii
                        quondam <persName><name ref="Iohannes Bonus">Iohannis Boni</name></persName>
                        et ceterorum hominum. Anno dominice incarnatjonis millesimo centesimo
                        quarto, pridie kalendas aprelis, indictione undecima. (L) <persName
                            key="#Writer #Notary"><name ref="Iohannes">Iohannes</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> domni imperatoris ibi fui et hunc brevem <rs
                            key="#Writer">scripsi</rs>. </ab>
                </div>
